        <h3 style="text-align: center;">UPDATE - <em>Mid-Aug 2020</em></h3>
    </div>
    <div class="card-body">
        <div class="card-text rounded bg-light text-dark p-2">
            <h5>Hey everybody! </h5>
            <h6>
            There are a lot of cool updates to SweatClause thanks to your feedback! The only down side is I needed to destroy your user profile to get it to work. I didn't want to recreate your profile on my end for security reasons. 
